title: FXH Makes Notable Cross Below Critical Moving Average - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Tuesday, shares of the First Trust Health Care AlphaDEX Fund ETF (Symbol: FXH) crossed below their 200 day moving average of $74.71, changing hands as low as $74.34 per share. First Trust Health Care AlphaDEX Fund shares are currently trading down about 1.2% on the day.
